text: This obsoletes IRM 11.3.20, Disclosure of Official Information, Personnel Records.

The material relating to program scope and objectives for Disclosure of Official Information, Personnel Records, previously contained in IRM 11.3.20.1, is incorporated into the new IRM 10.5.6.1, Privacy and Information Protection, Privacy Act, Program Scope and Objectives, revision dated
EFFECT ON OTHER DOCUMENTS This obsoletes IRM 11.3.20 dated August 21, 2018.
